## ğŸš€ **Quick Start**

### Prerequisites
- **Node.js**: 18.13.0 or higher
- **npm**: 9.0.0 or higher
- **Angular CLI**: 20.0.0 or higher

### Installation

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone <repository-url>
cd apex

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start development server
npm start
```

### Development Commands

```bash
# Development server (with auto-reload)
npm start                    # Runs on http://localhost:4200

# Production build
npm run build               # Optimized build for production

# Run tests
npm test                    # Unit tests with Karma
npm run test:coverage       # Generate test coverage report

# Lint and format
npm run lint               # ESLint analysis
npm run format             # Prettier formatting
```

## ğŸ“– **Usage Guide**

### **External Popovers**
Perfect for traditional help icons positioned outside form elements:

```html
<mat-form-field appearance="outline">
  <mat-label>Username</mat-label>
  <input matInput [(ngModel)]="username" placeholder="Enter username">
</mat-form-field>
<button
  mat-icon-button
  popoverTrigger="Username requirements:
  
â€¢ 3-20 characters
â€¢ Letters, numbers, and underscores only
â€¢ Must start with a letter
â€¢ Case sensitive"
  [popoverConfig]="{
    placement: 'bottom-start',
    showHeader: true,
    headerText: 'Username Help'
  }"
  aria-label="Help with username"
>
  <mat-icon>info_outline</mat-icon>
</button>
```

### **Inline Popovers (Recommended)**
Professional help icons positioned inside form elements using Material Design's `matSuffix`:

```html
<mat-form-field appearance="outline">
  <mat-label>Full Name</mat-label>
  <input matInput [(ngModel)]="fullName" placeholder="Enter full name">
  <button
    matSuffix
    mat-icon-button
    type="button"
    popoverTrigger="Full name guidelines:

â€¢ Use your legal name
â€¢ Include middle name if desired
â€¢ Format: First Middle Last
â€¢ Special characters supported"
    [popoverConfig]="{
      placement: 'bottom-end',
      showHeader: true,
      headerText: 'Name Guidelines'
    }"
    aria-label="Help with full name"
  >
    <mat-icon>help_outline</mat-icon>
  </button>
</mat-form-field>
```

### **Advanced Configuration**

```typescript
interface PopoverConfig {
  placement?: 'top' | 'bottom' | 'left' | 'right' | 'top-start' | 'bottom-end' | ...;
  showHeader?: boolean;
  headerText?: string;
  showClose?: boolean;
  maxWidth?: string;
  role?: 'dialog' | 'tooltip';
  trapFocus?: boolean;
  showCopy?: boolean;
  copyText?: string;
}
```

