## ğŸ¨ **Theming & Customization**

### **Material Design 3 Tokens**
The application uses Material Design 3 tokens for consistent theming:

```scss
// Custom theme variables
:root {
  --popover-bg: var(--md-sys-color-surface-container, #f3f3f3);
  --popover-fg: var(--md-sys-color-on-surface, #1d1b20);
  --popover-border: var(--md-sys-color-outline-variant, #c4c7c5);
}
```

### **Component Styling**
Leverage Material Design components with custom enhancements:

```scss
// Popover-specific styling
.popover {
  background: var(--popover-bg);
  color: var(--popover-fg);
  border: 1px solid var(--popover-border);
  border-radius: 12px;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
}
```

## â™¿ **Accessibility Standards**

### **WCAG 2.2 AAA Compliance**
- âœ… **Color Contrast**: 7:1 ratio for normal text, 4.5:1 for large text
- âœ… **Keyboard Navigation**: Full keyboard accessibility with visible focus indicators
- âœ… **Screen Readers**: Comprehensive ARIA implementation
- âœ… **Focus Management**: Proper focus trapping and restoration
- âœ… **Motion**: Respects `prefers-reduced-motion` settings

### **Accessibility Features**
```html
<!-- Proper ARIA implementation -->
<button
  matSuffix
  mat-icon-button
  type="button"
  [attr.aria-expanded]="isOpen"
  aria-haspopup="dialog"
  [attr.aria-describedby]="helpId"
  aria-label="Show help information"
>
  <mat-icon>help_outline</mat-icon>
</button>
```

